author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Bathroom exhaust fan removal tips…I take off the grill by squeezing the springs. I’m wearing the Ironclad Command A6 foam nitrile gloves, their ANSI A6 cut resistance keeps my hands safe from sharp sheet metal. I remove the fan body from the joist with a superbar and cut the wire because there was plenty up in the ceiling. Many thanks to Ironclad for sponsoring this video 🔥#exhaustfan #bathroomremodel #handsafety #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
